{"tid":1715660,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[又黎] 強國出現鼠疫病例","createTime":"2019-11-13T06:51:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T17:08:43.000Z","uid":171238,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0ead7c79f294ec23487bd6884f3fc772ac80eab5","tid":1715660,"uid":171238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T06:51:13.000Z","msg":"好擔心D老鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n內蒙古出現鼠疫病例，<strong>中國官方：一切盡在掌控中</strong><br />\n中國於11月12日晚上，發稿證實有兩名來自內蒙古患者感染「肺鼠疫」，並宣稱患者已在醫院接受完善的救治。對於疫情的控制，北京朝陽醫院相關負責人稱，「沒有必要恐慌，一切盡在掌控中」。<br />\n鼠疫是由鼠疫耶爾辛氏桿菌引起的疾病，通常在囓齒動物之間流行，但也會感染人類。具有起病快速、病程短、傳染性強等特性，一旦染上死亡率極高，是《中華人民共和國傳染病防治法》規定的甲類傳染病之一。"},{"pid":"e08e0f86ba89bb82acd5dce9b4bfabb118abf163","tid":1715660,"uid":43939,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T06:52:30.000Z","msg":"國之將亡...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19cb05556f4e0f8e1adc01174ef1bda8b032ba22","tid":1715660,"uid":48947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T06:56:38.000Z","msg":"black death<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00af11f4c2abda4ed6146b3f0e0405ea42c4e55e","tid":1715660,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T06:57:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">［文宣入！］返工搭鐵受襲、催淚彈影響健康、女學生返學俾狗捉，<strong>請文宣製圖向怕死嘅打工仔、家長、學生宣傳三罷</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n林鄭連續兩日叫大家唔好罷工罷課，證明罷工罷課係佢春袋，然而差佬不斷製造罷工罷課條件，文宣請行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請文宣組以<span style=\"color: red;\">黑警返工時間突襲旺角站無差別襲擊勤力返工人士</span>、<span style=\"color: gold;\">中午中環射催淚彈</span>、<span style=\"color: red;\">警察街上捉返學嘅女學生</span>、<span st